data.description: Welcome to this stunning horse farm nestled on 8.54 acres of picturesque land, offering breathtaking views that will captivate your heart. This equestrian paradise is a dream come true for horse enthusiasts and nature lovers alike. Let's take a closer look at what this remarkable property has to offer: This horse farm is fully equipped with top-notch equestrian facilities. You'll find well-maintained paddocks, spacious pastures, and a barn that's been designed with the comfort and well-being of your horses in mind. Whether you're a seasoned equestrian or just starting your journey, this farm is ready to meet your needs. Main Residence: The main residence is your charming countryside retreat. With large windows framing the breathtaking views, this home is bathed in natural light. Enjoy cozy evenings by the fireplace in the spacious living room, and savor meals in the well-appointed kitchen. The master bedroom offers a private oasis, and additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family and guests. Second Structure: The second structure, with its own utilities, could be used as a horse farm, artist studio, or even transitioned to a guest house if needed. Its design complements the main residence, and it opens up a world of opportunities for customization. This horse farm with its 8.54 acres of land and stunning views is a rare find that combines natural beauty, equestrian excellence, and comfortable living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own and live the countryside dream you've always envisioned. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the magic of this extraordinary horse farm for yourself!
